# Project Skills — Use by Context

Read the matching `SKILL.md` under `.agents/skills/<name>/` **before** acting. Do not improvise when a skill applies.

**Shell commands:** agent runs them per `.cursor/rules/agent-commands.mdc` — never ask user to type.

**Source of truth:** `final-install-list.md` and `PLAN.md` § Dev Tooling Setup.

## Active skills (16 kept + caveman)

| Skill | Trigger | Action |
|---|---|---|
| `hermes-dispatch` | After WP close, before merge, "hermes review", "ส่ง hermes" | Read skill → bundle + `hermes run` → parse VERDICT |
| `tdd` | New feature, bugfix, "red-green-refactor", DB/worker logic | Read skill → vertical-slice RED→GREEN |
| `diagnose` | Bug, failure, regression, "debug/diagnose" | Read skill → reproduce→minimise→fix loop |
| `review` | Review branch/PR/WIP, end of phase | Read skill → standards + spec review |
| `handoff` | End of session/phase, new agent pickup | Read skill → write handoff in `plan/` |
| `grill-me` | Stress-test a plan before coding | Read skill → interview user |
| `grill-with-docs` | Plan vs domain docs/ADR | Read skill → challenge against glossary |
| `prototype` | Explore design/UI/state before commit | Read skill → throwaway prototype |
| `improve-codebase-architecture` | Refactor, deepen modules, AI-navigability | Read skill → read `PLAN.md` first |
| `zoom-out` | Lost in details, need big picture | Read skill → architecture overview |
| `to-issues` | Break plan/spec into tickets | Read skill → tracer-bullet slices |
| `to-prd` | Turn conversation into PRD | Read skill → publish to issue tracker |
| `triage` | Create/triage issues, AFK agent prep | Read skill → state machine workflow |
| `setup-matt-pocock-skills` | Wire issue tracker for other skills | Read skill once per tracker choice |
| `setup-pre-commit` | User wants commit-time lint/test hooks | Read skill → Husky + lint-staged |
| `write-a-skill` | Author or edit a skill | Read skill → proper SKILL.md structure |
| `caveman` | User says "caveman", "less tokens", `/caveman*` | Read skill → terse output mode |

## Do NOT use (removed from this project)

`design-an-interface`, `qa`, `request-refactor-plan`, `ubiquitous-language`, `edit-article`, `obsidian-vault`, `writing-*`, `git-guardrails-claude-code`, `migrate-to-shoehorn`, `scaffold-exercises`, `teach` — unless user explicitly re-enables.

## Phase-aware defaults (`PLAN.md`)

| Phase | Prefer |
|---|---|
| 1 Scaffold+DB | `tdd`, `review`, `handoff` — **done**; report in `plan/phase1-report.md` |
| 2 Ingestor | `tdd` + `diagnose`; read `PLAN.md` ingestor section |
| 3–5 Worker | `tdd`; Context7 for faster-whisper/Ollama docs |
| 6 Alerter | `tdd`; Telegram outbound only |
| 7 Docker | `review` before merge |
| 8+ Observability/UI | `prototype` (dashboard), `review` |

Before any phase: read `PLAN.md` and latest `plan/handoff-*.md`. Do not re-litigate agreed decisions.
